#: ../../A/AFK.rst:5
msgid "AFK"
msgstr "AFK"

#: ../../A/AFK.rst:7
msgid ""
"[MUD] Abbrev. for \"Away From Keyboard\". Used to notify others that you "
"will be momentarily unavailable online. eg. \"Let's not go kill that frost "
"giant yet, I need to go AFK to make a phone call\". Often MUDs will have a "
"command to politely inform others of your absence when they try to talk with"
" you. The term is not restricted to MUDs, however, and has become common in "
"many chat situations, from IRC to Unix talk."
msgstr ""
"[MUD]「Away From "
"Keyboard(キーボードの前を離れている)」の略。一時的にオンラインで応答できなくなることを他人に知らせるのに使う。例:「あの霜の巨人を倒すのはまだやめておこう。電話をかけにAFKする必要があるんだ」。MUDには、誰かが話しかけてきたときに自分の不在を丁寧に知らせるコマンドがあることが多い。ただしこの語はMUDに限らず、IRCからUnixのtalkまで、多くのチャット状況で一般的になっている。"
